{"id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0019","text":"從未放開 這個苦悶被告","structure":{"line_index":19,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["痛苦","壓抑","無助"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["從未放開","苦悶","被告"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,5,4,9,2,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cung4","mei6","fong3","hoi1","ze5","go3","fu2","mun6","bei6","gou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"從未","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"放開","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"這個","pos":"DET"},{"text":"苦悶","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"被告","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"形容這種「苦悶」的狀態從未被「放開」，感覺自己像個「被告」般無助。"},"source":{"title":"屈到病","artists":["張學友"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5571","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0018","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0020","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0020","text":"沉睡片刻 都說低劣態度","structure":{"line_index":20,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["被誤解","負面評價","壓抑"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["沉睡","低劣態度"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,9,3,3,4,3,4,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["cam4","seoi6","pin2","hak1","dou1","syut3","dai1","lyut3","taai3","dou6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"沉睡","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"片刻","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"低劣","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"態度","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"即使是短暫的休息（沉睡），也被對方解讀為「低劣態度」，顯示對方總是負面解讀。"},"source":{"title":"屈到病","artists":["張學友"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5571","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0019","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0021","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0021","text":"每天 你說我語氣太粗","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":9},"semantics":{"themes":["被指責","語氣","溝通問題"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["每天","語氣太粗"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,3,5,4,5,5,4,4,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["mui5","tin1","nei5","syut3","ngo5","jyu5","hei3","taai3","cou1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"每天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"說","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"語氣","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"太粗","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"再次強調每天都被對方指責「語氣太粗」，是對方不斷的批評。"},"source":{"title":"屈到病","artists":["張學友"],"lyricists":["陳少琪"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5571","prev_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5byg5a2m5Y-L_NTU3MQ_0022","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
